针、Prometheus 指标端点\\n11: 5. **错误处理**: 统一的错误响应格式与日志记录\\n12: \\n13: ## Scope\\n14: \\n15: ### In Scope\\n16: \\n17: | Deliverable | Description |\\n18: |-------------|-------------|\\n19: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现，包括启动、关闭、配置 |\\n20: | `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由初始化与路由组管理 |\\n21: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/base.go` | 基础 Handler 接口定义 |\\n22: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health.go` | 健康检查与就绪探针实现 |\\n23: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging.go` | 请求日志中间件 |\\n24: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery.go` | Panic 恢复中间件 |\\n25: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors.go` | CORS 中间件（可选） |\\n26: | `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` | 请求/响应数据结构定义 |\\n27: \\n28: ### API Endpoints Framework\\n29: \\n30: ```\\n31: /api/v1/\\n32: ├── healthz          — 健康检查 (GET)\\n33: ├── readyz           — 就绪探针 (GET)\\n34: ├── sandboxes        — Sandbox CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\\n35: ├── sandboxclaims    — SandboxClaim CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\\n36: └── sessions         — Session 管理 (待后续 AR 实现)\\n37: ```\\n38: \\n39: ### Out of Scope\\n40: \\n4...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775843110219,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28780c7e5ffetTToawZ272Oixs\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787f68dd001zCzeUmy8cJQwYy\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787f51bb00192ZbbTO8yhTgFb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28780c7e5ffetTToawZ272Oixs\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-38869c0cfc624e6cb4d9c3b62ef9e796\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\\n12: \\n13: 定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\\n14: \\n15: ## Design\\n16: \\n17: ### Architecture\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: cmd/workload-manager/\\n21:     └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\\n22: pkg/workloadmanager/\\n23:     ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\\n24:     ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\\n25:     ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\\n26:     ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\\n27:     ├── doc.go                     — 包文档\\n28:     ├── handlers/\\n29:     │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\\n30:     │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\\n31:     └── middleware/\\n32:         ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\\n33:         ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\\n34:         └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\\n35: ```\\n36: \\n37: ### Kubernetes Client Integration\\n38: \\n39: WorkloadManager 使用 `client-go` 与 Kubernetes API 交互:\\n40: \\n41: | Client | API Group | Resource | Purpose |\\n42: |--------|-----------|----------|---------|\\n43: | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agent...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-005_ST-0.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775843106108,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28780b22cffeniJRMP4te8asP5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787f5a4e001rWbzvwyk7LOFz8\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787f4eb8001OE1Gmye2SFGpE0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28780b22cffeniJRMP4te8asP5\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll help you initialize a new OpenSpec change for the agentcube project. Let me first explore the project structure to understand the existing patterns.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775843106106,\"end\":1775843106106}}}\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775843108248,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28780b22cffeniJRMP4te8asP5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787f656a001g60W3SyW78MWbo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787f5eea001enrAZAgWiJ