n2: \\n3: 本规范定义了系统各核心组件必须实现的最小测试集。未通过以下测试用例的实现将被判定为“跑偏”。\\n4: \\n5: ## 1. Workload Manager (Go) - 核心准入测试\\n6: - **Func: `CreateSandbox`**\\n7:     - **Test-WM-1**: 必须 Mock Kubernetes Client，验证 `sandbox` 资源被正确创建。\\n8:     - **Test-WM-2**: 验证 Session 冲突处理（同名 Sandbox 冲突时返回 409 或恢复现有会话）。\\n9:     - **Test-WM-3**: 验证 Pod 状态同步逻辑。模拟 Pod 变为 `Running` 状态，验证 API 返回正确的 `Endpoint`。\\n10: - **Func: `DeleteSession`**\\n11:     - **Test-WM-4**: 验证物理资源的清理。确保调用了 K8s Delete API 且 Redis 记录同步删除。\\n12: \\n13: ## 2. Router (Go) - 高并发与安全测试\\n14: - **Middleware: `AuthMiddleware`**\\n15:     - **Test-RT-1**: 构造非法 JWT，验证返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\\n16:     - **Test-RT-2**: 构造过期 JWT，验证返回 `Token Expired`。\\n17: - **Proxy Logic: `HandleProxy`**\\n18:     - **Test-RT-3**: 模拟后端超时，验证 Proxy 正确处理 `Gateway Timeout` 且不崩溃。\\n19:     - **Test-RT-4**: 验证 Header 透传（Host, X-Forwarded-For 等）。\\n20: \\n21: ## 3. Session Store (Go) - 强一致性测试\\n22: - **Store Interface: `RedisStore` / `ValkeyStore`**\\n23:     - **Test-ST-1**: 验证对象序列化与反序列化（SessionInfo -> JSON -> SessionInfo）。\\n24:     - **Test-ST-2**: 并发写测试。模拟 100 个并发请求写入同一 Session，验证无 Data Race。\\n25: \\n26: ## 4. PicoD (Go) - 执行引擎隔离测试\\n27: - **Executor: `RunCode`**\\n28:     - **Test-PD-1**: 验证资源限制（如 OOM）。模拟大内存分配，验证进程被正确杀掉并返回错误。\\n29:     - **Test-PD-2**: 验证 Stdout 分块读取。处理超过 1MB 的输出，验证无缓冲区溢出。\\n...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842974355,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787d4a61001Dk7pdp8vs1tEii\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787d3ebc001ItMb0YV0FjbdAg\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_14182cfc9e8941b4bd6c41e9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\\n12: \\n13: Sandbox 创建处理器负责处理 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求，将用户的 AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter 定义转化为实际的 Sandbox（或 SandboxClaim）Kubernetes 资源，等待其进入 running 状态，解析 Pod IP 和入口点，持久化到 Store，并返回包含 sessionId 的响应。\\n14: \\n15: ## Architecture\\n16: \\n17: ### 组件交互\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: Client\\n21:   → POST /v1/agent-runtime 或 POST /v1/code-interpreter\\n22:     → authMiddleware（可选，EnableAuth=true 时生效）\\n23:       → handleAgentRuntimeCreate / handleCodeInterpreterCreate\\n24:         → 1. 解析并验证 CreateSandboxRequest\\n25:         → 2. 从 Informer 缓存获取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\\n26:         → 3. 构建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim 对象（workload_builder）\\n27:         → 4. StoreSandbox 占位记录\\n28:         → 5. WatchSandboxOnce 注册一次性 watcher\\n29:         → 6. 通过 dynamic client 创建 CR\\n30:         → 7. 等待 SandboxReconciler 通知 running（最长 2 分钟）\\n31:         → 8. 解析 Pod IP 和 entryPoints\\n32:         → 9. UpdateSandbox 更新完整信息\\n33:         → 10. 返回 CreateSandboxResponse\\n34: ```\\n35: \\n36: ### 关键依赖\\n37: \\n38: - **client...\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842974361,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787d5000001GTUPZwjhVEwgKE\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787d3ebc001ItMb0YV0FjbdAg\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_557ae16ac18742f085f5fbb9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\\n12: \\n13: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\\n14: \\n15: ## Architecture\\n16: \\n17: ### 组件分层\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: Client (SDK/CLI/Frontend)\\n21:   ↓ HTTPS\\n22: Gin Router (:8080)\\n23:   ↓\\n24: Middleware Stack\\n25:   ├─ LoggingMiddleware\\n26:   ├─ RecoveryMiddleware\\n27:   ├─ CORSMiddleware\\n28:   └─ AuthMiddleware (optional)\\n29:   ↓\\n30: HTTP Handlers\\n31:   ├─ AgentRuntime Handlers\\n32:   ├─ CodeInterpreter Handlers\\n33:   ├─ Health Handlers\\n34:   └─ Metrics Handler\\n35:   ↓\\n36: Service Layer (WorkloadManager Interface)\\n37:   ↓\\n38: Kubernetes Client Layer\\n39:   ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\\n40:   ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\\n41:   └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\\n42:   ↓\\n43: Kubernetes API Server\\n44: ```\\n45: \\n46: ### 目录结构\\n47: \\n48: ```\\n49: pkg/workloadmanager/\\n50: ├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful s...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842986033,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787d82fb001XUpPkxv2iYixBn\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787d75330016aMgvDj72L4MTU\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28782ed72ffegpf1AjZKbjAZFn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_1e6df767fbdd4e7eaa836ac1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Sandbox Orchestration Specification\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: Orchestrate agent sandboxes via Kubernetes CRDs (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter), a Gin HTTP API (workload manager), session persistence, garbage collection, and optional service-account authentication.\\n5: \\n6: ## Requirements\\n7: \\n8: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD schema and API registration\\n9: The system SHALL expose a namespaced `AgentRuntime` custom resource in API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`, with subresource `status`, print column `Age` from `.metadata.creationTimestamp`, and SHALL register list kind `AgentRuntimeList`.\\n10: \\n11: #### Scenario: Group version and resource naming\\n12: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes API client resolving the CRD\\n13: - **WHEN** the group, version, and kind are read from type metadata\\n14: - **THEN** `GroupVersion` is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, kind `AgentRuntime`, and GVR resource name is `agentruntimes`\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime spec fields and kubebuilder rules\\n17: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeSpec` with: `Ports` as `[]TargetPort` serialized under JSON key `targetPort`; required `Template` (`*SandboxTemplate`) under JSON key `podTemplate`; required `SessionTimeout` (`*metav1.Duration`) under `sessionTimeout` with kubebuilder default `\\\"15m\\\"`; require...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-004_ST-6.log:\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842920290,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28783ada5ffesC6B0aqgZEO6N3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787c859d001bxHjcfAAyYJLbP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787c7a53001Ukpl6xCau52Zm5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28783a