nput\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\\n12: \\n13: Sandbox 创建处理器负责处理 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求，将用户的 AgentRuntime 或 CodeInterpreter 定义转化为实际的 Sandbox（或 SandboxClaim）Kubernetes 资源，等待其进入 running 状态，解析 Pod IP 和入口点，持久化到 Store，并返回包含 sessionId 的响应。\\n14: \\n15: ## Architecture\\n16: \\n17: ### 组件交互\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: Client\\n21:   → POST /v1/agent-runtime 或 POST /v1/code-interpreter\\n22:     → authMiddleware（可选，EnableAuth=true 时生效）\\n23:       → handleAgentRuntimeCreate / handleCodeInterpreterCreate\\n24:         → 1. 解析并验证 CreateSandboxRequest\\n25:         → 2. 从 Informer 缓存获取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\\n26:         → 3. 构建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim 对象（workload_builder）\\n27:         → 4. StoreSandbox 占位记录\\n28:         → 5. WatchSandboxOnce 注册一次性 watcher\\n29:         → 6. 通过 dynamic client 创建 CR\\n30:         → 7. 等待 SandboxReconciler 通知 running（最长 2 分钟）\\n31:         → 8. 解析 Pod IP 和 entryPoints\\n32:         → 9. UpdateSandbox 更新完整信息\\n33:         → 10. 返回 CreateSandboxResponse\\n34: ```\\n35: \\n36: ### 关键依赖\\n37: \\n38: - **client...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842806895,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287857f55ffeAzY6dJippQ21pG\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787ac70c001EY35PsIauMczsp\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787ab2bd001iSgwNH3JjHj8dM\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287857f55ffeAzY6dJippQ21pG\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_745f003b8616455fafaecdac\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |\\n6: |------|-------|\\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n9: | Language | Go |\\n10: | Size | M |\\n11: | Stage | ST-1 completed |\\n12: \\n13: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架提供 Kubernetes-native 的 HTTP API，用于管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 工作负载。该服务封装了 client-go 的复杂性，为 Python SDK、CLI 工具和其他消费者提供简化的 RESTful 接口。\\n14: \\n15: ## Architecture\\n16: \\n17: ### 组件分层\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: Client (SDK/CLI/Frontend)\\n21:   ↓ HTTPS\\n22: Gin Router (:8080)\\n23:   ↓\\n24: Middleware Stack\\n25:   ├─ LoggingMiddleware\\n26:   ├─ RecoveryMiddleware\\n27:   ├─ CORSMiddleware\\n28:   └─ AuthMiddleware (optional)\\n29:   ↓\\n30: HTTP Handlers\\n31:   ├─ AgentRuntime Handlers\\n32:   ├─ CodeInterpreter Handlers\\n33:   ├─ Health Handlers\\n34:   └─ Metrics Handler\\n35:   ↓\\n36: Service Layer (WorkloadManager Interface)\\n37:   ↓\\n38: Kubernetes Client Layer\\n39:   ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface)\\n40:   ├─ informers (SharedInformerFactory)\\n41:   └─ listers (AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister)\\n42:   ↓\\n43: Kubernetes API Server\\n44: ```\\n45: \\n46: ### 目录结构\\n47: \\n48: ```\\n49: pkg/workloadmanager/\\n50: ├── server.go              # Gin server setup, router configuration, graceful s...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775842906772,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287857f55ffeAzY6dJippQ21pG\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d787ae015001dlsRt80phVj1VK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d787accb8001QbR57iz4tQNwau\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287857f55ffeAzY6dJippQ21pG\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_6c6514b749a54222b78a147d\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/delta-spec.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Delta Specification\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nDefine the sandbox creation processor implementation for handling `POST /v1/agent-runtime` and `POST /v1/code-interpreter` requests. The processor transforms AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter definitions into actual Sandbox/SandboxClaim Kubernetes resources, waits for running state, resolves Pod IP and entry points, persists to Store, and returns sessionId.\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: CreateSandboxRequest validation\\n\\nThe system SHALL implement `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate()` in `pkg/common/types.go`. Validation SHALL check: `Kind` is \\\"AgentRuntime\\\" or \\\"CodeInterpreter\\\", `Namespace` is non-empty, `Name` is non-empty.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Valid request validation\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a CreateSandboxRequest with `Kind: \\\"AgentRuntime\\\"`, `Name: \\\"my-runtime\\\"`, `Namespace: \\\"default\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** `Validate()` is called\\n- **THEN** the method SHALL return nil (no error)\\n\\n#### Scenario: Missing name validation\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a CreateSandboxRequest with `Name: \\\"\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** `Validate()` is called\\n- **THEN** the method SHALL return `fmt.Errorf(\\\"name is required\\\")`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Missing namespace validation\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a CreateSandboxRequest with `Namespace: \\\"\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** `Validate()` is called\\n- **THEN** the method SHALL return `fmt.Errorf(\\\"namespace is required\\\")`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invalid kind validation\\n\\n- **GIVEN** a CreateSandboxRequest with `Kind: \\\"Unknown\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** `Validate()` is call...\n\n/home/dsj/benc