- **Timeout defaults**: TTL, idle, max lifetime, session, grace period\n- **Port constants**: HTTP (80), HTTPS (443), CodeInterpreter (8888)\n- **Resource defaults**: CPU (100m/1000m), Memory (128Mi/1Gi)\n- **Finalizers**: Sandbox cleanup, resource cleanup\n- **Event reasons**: Created, Updated, Deleted, Failed, etc.\n\n#### 3. Code Generation\n- ✅ DeepCopy methods generated via `controller-gen` in `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- ✅ All shared types have proper DeepCopy/DeepCopyInto/DeepCopyObject methods\n\n#### 4. Testing\n- ✅ Unit tests created: `common_types_test.go`\n- ✅ Compilation verified: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` succeeds\n- ✅ Compatible with AR-001 (AgentRuntime) and AR-002 (CodeInterpreter)\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ What Was Deferred\n\n| Item | Reason |\n|------|--------|\n| **Controller-gen webhook markers** | Out of scope — webhook validation deferred to future AR |\n| **CRD manifest generation** | Deferred to AR-001/AR-002 integration phase |\n| **Integration tests** | N/A for shared types — to be tested via AR-001/AR-002 usage |\n| **golangci-lint validation** | Deferred to CI pipeline setup |\n| **hack/boilerplate.go.txt** | Standard header already applied manually |\n\n---\n\n### 📊 Statistics\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Files created | 2 (`common_types.go`, `constants.go`) |\n| Lines of code | ~717 lines (354 + 363) |\n| Shared types defined | 18 |\n| Constants defined | 100+ |\n| Test files | 1 (`common_types_test.go`) |\n| Generated files | 1 (`zz_generated.deepcopy.go`) |\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 References\n\n- **Depends on**: AR-001 (AgentRuntime types), AR-002 (CodeInterpreter types)\n- **Used by**: AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP framework), AR-005 (Sandbox creation processor)\n- **API Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`","time":{"start":1775843320375,"end":1775843320375}}}
